title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 16 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Feb 16 2022
description:
Sara Carter of Fox News joins C&B to tell us who the Canadian truckers really are and what they're expecting from Trudeau's crackdown. Psaki refuses to comment on Durham revelations. Pennsylvania senate candidate Dave McCormick joins Clay and Buck, about what's motivating PA voters, how Biden is failing, hot-button school issues. C&B talk fashion choices for their trip to Mar-a-Lago next week to talk with President Trump and preview tomorrow's show featuring special guests Kathryn Limbaugh and Sean Hannity.
